      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 19:33:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通胀数据公布后市场预期美联储 12 月降息概率达 80%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/traders-boost-bets-on-december-fed-cut-after-in-line-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在通胀数据符合预期后，交易员们加大了对美联储下个月将利率再次降息四分之一个百分点的押注，刺激美国国债上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/traders-boost-bets-on-december-fed-cut-after-in-line-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 13:55:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国燃料组织警告称，若无信贷指导，油价将上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/fuel-groups-warn-of-higher-prices-without-tax-credit-certainty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[能源、农业和运输领域的三十多个贸易团体表示，美国政府缺乏对税收抵免的指导，使美国人面临燃油价格上涨的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/fuel-groups-warn-of-higher-prices-without-tax-credit-certainty</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
